corecluster (16.06.24) stable; urgency=low

  * Cleaned up config file
  * Added LOG_PREFIX to config file
  * Experimental IPv6 support
  * Updated support for new template settings in Django 1.8
  * Configuration API
  * OSPF_TOKEN setting moved from config.py to corenetwork's config.py
  * Updated behavior of image, node and vm agents
  * Added support for random generator via libvirt
  * Fixed network allocation
  * Fixed task handling in queue - objects should be smaller
  * Added new auth method for authorizing by token in default auth algorithm. Token could be sent in form: tokenid-hashmethod-salt-tokenhash
  * Support for systemd
  * Automatic checks for updates
  * Removed timedelta field

